videos.description: Maryland takes the lead and Lourawls Nairn Jr. connects with Miles Bridges on the alley-oop dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: Bridges answers with alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Michigan State moves the ball around and Kenny Goins sinks a corner 3-pointer to tie the game early.
videos.headline: Goins makes key corner 3-pointer for Spartans

videos.description: Kevin Huerter works his way around the defender and draws contact as he makes the basket for Maryland.
videos.headline: Huerter uses spin move on and-1 bucket

videos.description: Nick Ward blocks a shot from behind to shut down the Terrapins.
videos.headline: Ward denies Fernando with big block

videos.description: Miles Bridges finds Matt McQuaid for back-to-back 3-pointers and the Michigan State bench loves it.
videos.headline: McQuaid pumps up Spartans with back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Cassius Winston gets a pass to Xavier Tillman who lays it in to add to Michigan State's eventual 15-3 run.
videos.headline: Spartans go on big run to end 1st half

videos.description: Jaren Jackson Jr. blocks Dion Wiley's shot to prevent a Maryland bucket.
videos.headline: Jackson Jr. blocks jump shot

videos.description: Michigan State uses good ball movement and Miles Bridges finishes with a nice jump shot.
videos.headline: Bridges makes smooth jumper
